COVID-19 Status

As of 7:19AM PT today, over 1.4 million Canadians have tested positive for COVID-19. Sadly, 26.4 thousand have died.

In the last day, 311 new infections were reported and 9 deaths. This is trending downwards.

Fortunately, 40 million doses of the vaccine have been administered. For those 12 years and older, 78.1% have their 1st shot and 42.3% are fully vaccinated!

Vaccination is speeding up, but there are 9.4 million doses in the freezer. It currently takes ~19 days for new deliveries to get into arms. At the current rate, all Canadians aged 12+ should have the first dose by Oct-05 and fully vaccinated by Aug-21. There is no approved vaccine for children aged 11 or younger.
